	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_000984_0001"/><!--pb/@n='10r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>57 Sloane St</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">30<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> March</p>
<lb/><p rend="right">1857</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Murray</persName></p>
<lb/><p><persName>Adams</persName> goes 
<lb/>the "whole hog" you 
<lb/>see, dedicated to 
<lb/>the Missionary Society 
<lb/>not however by 
<lb/>permission I hope. 
<lb/><persName>Sir Roderick</persName>
<lb/>thinks we ought 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_000984_0002"/><!--pb/@n='10v'--> 
<lb/>to put an advertisement 
<lb/>in the Times as 
<lb/>well. I have not 
<lb/>seen the reply in 
<lb/>the Athenaeum, can 
<lb/>you let me see it 
<lb/>if it be necessary 
<lb/>to reply<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>I send I - XIII 
<lb/>keeping back 
<lb/><!-- This is not a symbol - it's just a marking he put to highlight  the 'X' -->X as I am about 
<lb/>to sweeten it as I 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_000984_0003"/><!--pb/@n='11r'--> 
<lb/>been engaged all 
<lb/>day in doing to 
<lb/>other parts. </p>
<lb/><p><choice><reg>T</reg><orig>t</orig></choice>here is a tree 
<lb/>in the plate of the 
<lb/>Falls which I 
<lb/>objected to before 
<lb/>it is of this shape 
<lb/><figure><!--<graphic url="LETT530-1.gif"/>--><figDesc/></figure> now I wanted 
<lb/>it thus <figure><!--<graphic url="LETT530-2.gif"/>--><figDesc/></figure> with 
<lb/>foliage on these 
<lb/>little branches alone 
<lb/>the enormous 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_000984_0004"/><!--pb/@n='11v'--> 
<lb/>arms are always 
<lb/>seen distinctly even 
<lb/>at a distance. You 
<lb/>can have some 
<lb/>more pieces as 
<lb/>soon as I look 
<lb/>over the errata 
<lb/>and a few more 
<lb/>for your friend<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>Could an injunction 
<lb/>not be got with 
<lb/>case against this? </p>
<lb/><p rend="center">Yours &amp;c </p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><persName>D Livingstone</persName></p> <addSpan spanTo="#p10r-01" place="marginleft"><!--addSpan/@place='left margin of fol. 10r'--></addSpan>
<lb/><p><placeName>Lake Nygami</placeName> might be improved. <choice><reg>M</reg><orig>m</orig></choice>y 
<lb/>jacket was always short - &amp; blue cloth cap<reg>.</reg></p><anchor xml:id="p10r-01"/>
			
</div>
